OL,3,CThe household habits could be causing
OL,4,Cmajor sewage blocks in London
OL,6,FWatch as Thames Water uncover a large
OL,7,Ffatberg.
OL,9,FLondoners don't know what they can and
OL,10,Fcannot pour down sinks and toilets,
OL,11,Faccording to Thames Water.
OL,13,FThe water company carried out research
OL,14,Finto the cause of the more than 74,000
OL,15,Fblockages it clears annually -
OL,16,Fsomething that it says costs them #40
OL,17,Fmillion every year.
