OL,3,CThe household habits could be causing
OL,4,Cmajor sewage blocks in London
OL,6,FThames Water say mistakes could cost
OL,7,Fhundreds of pounds each to fix this
OL,8,Fwinter, with residents across London
OL,9,Fand the Thames Valley pouring milk,
OL,10,Fmeat juices and oil down kitchen sinks.
OL,12,FThese substances over time increase
OL,13,Fthe risk of so-called 'fatbergs' -
OL,14,Fmassive blockages that can cause major
OL,15,Fsewage disruption.
OL,17,FIn extreme cases, sewage can spill out
OL,18,Finto streets and homes.
