OL,3,CThe household habits could be causing
OL,4,Cmajor sewage blocks in London
OL,6,FOne of the largest blockages that the
OL,7,Fcompany cleared in 2025 was was 100-
OL,8,Ftonne, 125-metre-long fatberg in the
OL,9,Fcapital.
OL,11,FThames Water's research also indicated
OL,12,Fthat 34% of people put oily plates in
OL,13,Fthe dishwasher, and 29% rinse fats,
OL,14,Foils or grease away with hot water or
OL,15,Fwashing-up liquid, innocently
OL,16,Fbelieving it prevents clogs.
