OL,3,CThe household habits could be causing
OL,4,Cmajor sewage blocks in London
OL,6,FIt's also the case in the bathroom - a
OL,7,Ffifth of Londoners admitted to
OL,8,Fflushing wet wipes down the toilet.
OL,9,FThe water giant blames this on
OL,10,F'confusing labelling' for toiletries.
OL,12,FOther common culprits include kitchen
OL,13,Froll and sanitary towels.
OL,15,FPeople are encouraged to bin fats and
OL,16,Favoid putting things that don't belong
OL,17,Fdown the toilet or the sink.
